George Gebhardt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Gebhardt 0 George Gebhardt (September 21 1879 – May 2, 1919) was a Swiss-born American silent film actor. He appeared in 128 films between 1908 and 1922. He was born in Basel, Switzerland and died in Edendale, Los Angeles from tuberculosis.
